	* mkf/script/config.guess, kiklib/script/config.guess,
	  script/config.guess: updated (timestamp='2007-07-22')

	* mkf/script/config.sub, kiklib/script/config.sub,
	  script/config.sub: updated (timestamp='2007-06-28')

