	* rewrite manpage for 2002-05-30 changes.

2002-05-30 Araki Ken <arakiken@users.sf.net>

	* string to be output can be defined in ~/.mlterm/key like
	  Control+F1="foobar".
	* rgb of highlighted 8 colors can be defined as hl_{black|white|...}
	  in ~/.mlterm/color.

